name: Peeked Interest
overview:
Peeked Interest is a breakthrough new service that allows us to capture everyday moments, share them with the world and make connections with people who we may never have been able to meet. We’ll discover and meet new people through our photos and bring excitement, curiosity, and genuine (always welcome) compliments to our everyday lives.

For many of us, our busy lives don’t always lend themselves to meeting new people; every day we miss opportunities to make contact with people, who for whatever reason happen to “peek” our interest. Perhaps we are a little shy or maybe the situation simply does not lend itself to making that initial contact. Peeked Interest is a unique way to make that first contact. Snap a photo, write a description and post for the world to see.

Nothing like this has been done before and we are excited to pave the way into a future where our reality becomes more digitally integrated. Undoubtedly we will have our critics, but we will remain true to our ethics and final goal of creating a service that connects people outside of our current social graphs.
